444
00:31:51.362 --> 00:31:52.870
I...

445
00:31:53.312 --> 00:31:54.442
Wednesday?

446
00:31:54.542 --> 00:31:56.370
I can't wait that long.

447
00:31:56.651 --> 00:31:58.495
